Technologies to pick up:
* A little bit of javascript (MDN is great resource,https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript)
* Node JS
* How NPM works (very easy).

NPM Modules to Use:
* ExpressJS  (https://www.npmjs.com/package/express)
* MySQL   (https://www.npmjs.com/package/mysql)
* lodash
*** https://www.npmjs.com/  Search for more modules.

Javascript IDEs (opensource)
* http://brackets.io/
* https://code.visualstudio.com/
* https://atom.io/
* http://nuclide.io/
** lots to choose from and they all work the same way, it's up to preference.

